<hr data-start="695" data-end="698">
<h3 data-section-id="tpmp9" data-start="700" data-end="728">Kani mee original doubt:</h3>
<blockquote data-start="730" data-end="771">
<p data-start="732" data-end="771"><strong data-start="732" data-end="771">"admin_login.html enduku vastundi?"</strong></p>
</blockquote>
<p data-start="773" data-end="824">Mee <code data-start="777" data-end="785">app.py</code> lo ledu.<br>
Mee <code data-start="799" data-end="810">home.html</code> lo kuda ledu.</p>
<p data-start="826" data-end="922">Kabatti adi almost certainly <strong data-start="855" data-end="873"><code data-start="857" data-end="871">predict.html</code></strong>, <strong data-start="875" data-end="892"><code data-start="877" data-end="890">submit.html</code></strong>, leda vere HTML file lo undi.</p>
<h3 data-section-id="1e7jffj" data-start="924" data-end="958">Naaku ippudu ee 2 files pampu:</h3>
<ol data-start="959" data-end="993">
<li data-section-id="1hrr90" data-start="959" data-end="976">
<p data-start="962" data-end="976"><code data-start="962" data-end="976">predict.html</code></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1suj926" data-start="977" data-end="993">
<p data-start="980" data-end="993"><code data-start="980" data-end="993">submit.html</code></p>
</li>
</ol>
<p data-start="995" data-end="1073">Alage browser lo <strong data-start="1012" data-end="1027">exact error</strong> ni copy-paste cheyyi (leda screenshot pampu).</p>
