<p data-start="360" data-end="414">Idi match kaadu. <code data-start="377" data-end="386">predict</code> route POST accept cheyyadu.</p>
<h3 data-section-id="4hjl8c" data-start="416" data-end="447">Naaku oka screenshot pampu:</h3>
<ol data-start="448" data-end="546">
<li data-section-id="9rekox" data-start="448" data-end="491">
<p data-start="451" data-end="491">Browser lo vachina <strong data-start="470" data-end="490">exact error page</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1wpate7" data-start="492" data-end="546">
<p data-start="495" data-end="546">Browser address bar kuda kanipinchela undali (URL).</p>
</li>
</ol>
<p data-start="548" data-end="580">Leda error ni copy-paste cheyyi.</p>
<p data-start="582" data-end="594">Udaharanaki:</p>
<ul data-start="595" data-end="696">
<li data-section-id="kg915d" data-start="595" data-end="651">
<p data-start="597" data-end="651"><code data-start="597" data-end="651">jinja2.exceptions.TemplateNotFound: admin_login.html</code></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="xxxjaj" data-start="652" data-end="678">
<p data-start="654" data-end="678"><code data-start="654" data-end="678">405 Method Not Allowed</code></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="us4l7" data-start="679" data-end="696">
<p data-start="681" data-end="696"><code data-start="681" data-end="696">404 Not Found</code></p>
</li>
</ul>
<h3 data-section-id="12mfkw6" data-start="698" data-end="744">Alage project folder structure kuda pampu:</h3>
