<h3 data-section-id="g34b5w" data-start="88" data-end="98">Error:</h3>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="99" data-end="157"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="contents"><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-16f983c9.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>_pickle.UnpicklingError: invalid load key, '{'</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="159" data-end="234">Idi almost <strong data-start="170" data-end="178">100%</strong> <code data-start="179" data-end="195">loan_model.pkl</code> file valid pickle file kaadani artham.</p>
<p data-start="236" data-end="331"><code data-start="236" data-end="251">pickle.load()</code> binary model file expect chestundi. Kani mee <code data-start="297" data-end="313">loan_model.pkl</code> lo <code data-start="317" data-end="320">{</code> undi ante:</p>
<ul data-start="332" data-end="485">
<li data-section-id="127p8mh" data-start="332" data-end="356">
<p data-start="334" data-end="356">JSON file ayi undachu.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="5ruprg" data-start="357" data-end="381">
<p data-start="359" data-end="381">Text file ayi undachu.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="tqcl2z" data-start="382" data-end="450">
<p data-start="384" data-end="450">GitHub nundi HTML page save chesi <code data-start="418" data-end="424">.pkl</code> ani rename chesi undachu.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="o39y1m" data-start="451" data-end="485">
<p data-start="453" data-end="485">Leda <code data-start="458" data-end="464">.pkl</code> file corrupt ayindi.</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="487" data-end="490">
<h2 data-section-id="171fm51" data-start="492" data-end="528">Step 1: File size check cheyyandi</h2>
<p data-start="530" data-end="582"><code data-start="530" data-end="546">loan_model.pkl</code> meeda <strong data-start="553" data-end="581">Right Click → Properties</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="584" data-end="594">Cheppandi:</p>
<ul data-start="595" data-end="620">
<li data-section-id="hfbe0c" data-start="595" data-end="620">
<p data-start="597" data-end="620"><strong data-start="597" data-end="612">Size entha?</strong> (KB/MB)</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="622" data-end="625">
<h2 data-section-id="14t145c" data-start="627" data-end="671">Step 2: File ni Notepad lo open cheyyandi</h2>
<p data-start="673" data-end="719"><code data-start="673" data-end="689">loan_model.pkl</code> ni Notepad lo open cheyyandi.</p>
<h3 data-section-id="eplgsz" data-start="721" data-end="731">Case A</h3>
