<p data-start="1503" data-end="1672">Kani dataset lo <strong data-start="1519" data-end="1537">12–13 features</strong> untayi (Gender, Married, Education, Property_Area, etc.). Ala train chesina model ni 5 features tho predict cheyyalem. Error vastundi.</p>
