<h3 data-section-id="tmtjer" data-start="39" data-end="90">Jupyter Notebook lo code ekkada paste cheyyali?</h3>
<ol data-start="92" data-end="467">
<li data-section-id="1o49g68" data-start="92" data-end="131">
<p data-start="95" data-end="131"><strong data-start="95" data-end="115">Jupyter Notebook</strong> open cheyyandi.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="13sr9hr" data-start="132" data-end="180">
<p data-start="135" data-end="180"><strong data-start="135" data-end="162">New → Python 3 Notebook</strong> create cheyyandi.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="j3q5gn" data-start="181" data-end="306">
<p data-start="184" data-end="306">Notebook open ayyaka first cell untundi. Lekapothe <strong data-start="235" data-end="247"><code data-start="237" data-end="245">+ Code</code></strong> button meeda click chesi kotha code cell create cheyyandi.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="13b4mdt" data-start="307" data-end="380">
<p data-start="310" data-end="380">Aa code cell lo nenu ichina complete training code ni paste cheyyandi.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1ylzn7m" data-start="381" data-end="467">
<p data-start="384" data-end="467"><strong data-start="384" data-end="401">Shift + Enter</strong> press cheyyandi (leda toolbar lo <strong data-start="435" data-end="442">Run</strong> button click cheyyandi).</p>
</li>
</ol>
<p data-start="469" data-end="491">Visual ga ila untundi:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="493" data-end="903"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="contents"><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-16f983c9.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>+------------------------------------------------------+</span><br><span>| import pandas as pd                                  |</span><br><span>| import pickle                                        |</span><br><span>| from sklearn.model_selection import ...              |</span><br><span>| ...                                                  |</span><br><span>| print("loan_model.pkl created successfully!")        |</span><br><span>+------------------------------------------------------+</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="905" data-end="957">Aa cell run ayyaka <code data-start="924" data-end="940">loan_model.pkl</code> create avutundi.</p>
<h3 data-section-id="jsl6on" data-start="959" data-end="976">Oka question:</h3>
<p data-start="978" data-end="1060">Meeru <strong data-start="984" data-end="1004">Jupyter Notebook</strong> use chestunnara? Leda <strong data-start="1027" data-end="1043">Google Colab</strong> use chestunnara?</p>
<ul data-start="1062" data-end="1147">
<li data-section-id="ditgd3" data-start="1062" data-end="1101">
<p data-start="1064" data-end="1101"><strong data-start="1064" data-end="1084">Jupyter Notebook</strong> aithe cheppandi.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="lho7wu" data-start="1102" data-end="1147">
<p data-start="1104" data-end="1147"><strong data-start="1104" data-end="1120">Google Colab</strong> aithe adhi kuda cheppandi.</p>
</li>
</ul>
