<h2 data-section-id="1b78ga4" data-start="535" data-end="550">⚠️ Important</h2>
<p data-start="552" data-end="611"><code data-start="552" data-end="568">loan_model.pkl</code> create ayindi ante oka issue solve ayindi.</p>
<p data-start="613" data-end="764"><strong data-start="613" data-end="621">Kani</strong> mee current <code data-start="634" data-end="642">app.py</code> inka correct kaadu. Endukante model <strong data-start="679" data-end="694">11 features</strong> expect chestundi, kani <code data-start="718" data-end="726">app.py</code> <strong data-start="727" data-end="741">5 features</strong> maatrame pampisthundi.</p>
<p data-start="766" data-end="818">Kabatti next run chesinappudu ilaanti error ravachu:</p>
<ul data-start="820" data-end="893">
<li data-section-id="1tqqzzc" data-start="820" data-end="893">
<p data-start="822" data-end="893"><code data-start="822" data-end="893">X has 5 features, but RandomForestClassifier is expecting 11 features</code></p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="895" data-end="910"><strong data-start="895" data-end="910">Adi normal.</strong></p>
<p data-start="912" data-end="953">👉 <strong data-start="915" data-end="953">Ippudu <code data-start="924" data-end="939">python app.py</code> run cheyyi.</strong></p>
<p data-start="955" data-end="1010"><strong data-start="955" data-end="1010">E error vachindo screenshot leda copy-paste cheyyi.</strong></p>
