<p data-start="78" data-end="176">Ante notebook <strong data-start="92" data-end="106">ade folder</strong> lo run ayindi. Ante <code data-start="127" data-end="143">loan_model.pkl</code> <strong data-start="144" data-end="175">ade folder lo create avvali</strong>.</p>
