<p data-start="266" data-end="299"><code data-start="266" data-end="282">loan_model.pkl</code> create avvaledu.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="ahx0pa" data-start="300" data-end="361">
<p data-start="303" data-end="361">Vere peru tho save ayindi (example: <code data-start="339" data-end="359">loan_model.pkl.pkl</code>).</p>
</li>
</ol>
