" data-end="59">Perfect. Manam <strong data-start="15" data-end="37">SkillWallet Task 1</strong> nunchi start cheddam.</p>
<h2 data-section-id="jvlyy2" data-start="61" data-end="112">Task 1: ER Diagram (Entity Relationship Diagram)</h2>
